Package: colormod
Title: Simple Tools for Manipulating Colors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(family="Connelly", given="Brian D.",
    email="bdc@bconnelly.net", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Description: colormod provides simple and consistent functions for extracting
    and manipulating individual components of colors using 'colorspace'. With a
    focus on portability, colormod works primarily with hex triplets.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.2)
Imports: 
    assertthat,
    grDevices,
Suggests:
    testthat
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/briandconnelly/colormod
BugReports: https://github.com/briandconnelly/colormod/issues
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
